ink?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2384736&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GhZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=7d6d2eed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2384736</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T09:15:30.000Z","msg":"世界上只有以聯合國為核心的國際體系，規則只有以聯合國憲章宗旨為基礎的國際關係基本準則。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國咪又係共匪同佢班非洲窮國手下話事。仲有人信咩？"},{"pid":"0ccb726ca943b5517af11b96812ee8390bdbd8a2","tid":2462824,"uid":218353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e05f0fc59c0891479bd2a9e39f90fa512da034e","tid":2462824,"uid":293296,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T08:52:08.000Z","msg":"可唔可以成熟啲呀<br />\n成個小學雞咁嘅口吻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T09:15:41.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n口交部算唔算係因國廢言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6079481392f35c0775dd1bd2b3160bb492e79eb9","tid":2462824,"uid":301820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T09:16:29.000Z","msg":"不正常人類國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf1a4ea4ea9efa4b1a8997c990c13c952f3aaa90","tid":2462824,"uid":286131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e73d2dfdc84e020836267584a8536b19cfd567d","tid":2462824,"uid":204533,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T08:52:50.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">中國沒資格做國際關係的教師爺</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T09:17:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />10/10"},{"pid":"e7cbf8ba4a92dba8819ccc190f1ca9bb91b3dbbe","tid":2462824,"uid":145837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e23a44430d1c48f7222dde5f44993ef6e772d466","tid":2462824,"uid":152476,"lik